quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  8,45,"ya 'ayuha aladhin sddaqu allah warasulah waeamiluu bshreh, 'iidha laqitum jamaeat min 'ahl alkufr qad astedu lqtalkm, fathbutuu wala tnhzmu enhm, wadhkuruu allah kthyrana daein mbthlyn li'iinzal alnasr ealaykum walzzafar bedwkm; likay tfwzu"
  8,46,"waltzmu taeat allah wtaet rasulih fi kl ahwalkm, wala tkhtlfu fttfrq klmtkm wtkhtlf qlwbkm, ftdefu watadhhab quatikum wnsrkm, wasbiruu eind lqah aledw. 'iina allah mae alsaabirin balewn walnsr waltayyd, walan ykhdhlhm"
  8,47,wla takunuu mithl almushrikin aladhin kharajuu min baladihim kbrana wrya'an; lymneu alnaas ean aldukhul fi din allh. wallah bima yaemalun muhit la yaghib eanh shy'
  8,48,"wadhkru hin hssan alshaytan lilmushrikin ma jawu lah wama hmmu bh, waqal lhm: ln yghlbkm ahd alyawm, fa'iiniy nasrkm, falamaa tqabl alfryqan: almushrikun wamaeahum alshytan, walmslmwn wamaeahum almlaykt, raje alshaytan mudbrana, waqal llmshrkyn: 'iiniy bari' mnkm, 'iiniy 'araa ma la tarawn min almalayikat aladhin jawu mddana llmslmyn, 'iiniy 'akhaf allh, fkhdhlhm wtbra mnhm. wallah shadid aleiqab liman easah walam yatub tawbatan nswhana"